I fail to see how this relates to the HubSpot Developer Community to be honest.

Nonetheless you can try to use a different network to see if this still happens.
Or update composer.
Or if this is specific to packagist you could set a different repository source in your composer.json
```{
  "repositories": [
    {
      "<http://packagist.org|packagist.org>": {
        "type": "composer",
        "url": "<https://packagist.jp>"
      }
    }
  ]
}```
